io.nem.sdk.api

Class RepositoryFactoryConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nem.sdk.api.RepositoryFactoryConfiguration

  • public class RepositoryFactoryConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    This bean helps the user to create RepositoryFactory. The only required attribute is the network base url. If the user knows the other values, they can be provided to allow a better offline capability. If the values are not provided, the RepositoryFactory will load and cache them using the repositories
    See Also:
    RepositoryFactory, RepositoryFactoryBase
